      "widgets_values": [
        "wan2.7-r2v",
        "Steadicam tracking shot from the side. A wide underwater boulevard lined with glowing lanterns and coral archways, fish drifting between the buildings. The steampunk woman (image1) walks slowly along the street, one hand trailing along a brass railing, head turning to take it all in. The robot (image2) walks beside her, slightly behind. Camera tracks them from the right. Woman: \"How long has it been here?\" Robot: \"Four hundred and twelve years.\" Woman (stopping): \"And no one found it?\" Robot: \"No one looked.\"\n",
